<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #222;">
    <p>Dear {{data.te_name}},</p>
    <p>
        The costing of the Tender
        {{data.tender_name}}, has been edited and approved for bidding. I have prepared the tender documents with the best of my understanding of the technical documents, the scope
        of work, and the quotations received from the vendor. Please submit the Tender using the costing sheet.
    </p>
    <p>Link: <a href="{{data.costing_sheet_link}}">Costing sheet</a></p>

    <p><strong>Tender Value (GST Inclusive):</strong> {{data.tender_value}}</p>

    <table width="100%" cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0"
        style="border: 1px solid #444; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">#</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Approved Final Price (GST Incl.)</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Approved Receipt (Pre GST)</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Approved Budget (Pre GST)</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Approved Gross Margin %</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #444; background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">TL Remarks</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each data.details}}
            <tr>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.index}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.approvedFinalPrice}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.approvedReceipt}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.approvedBudget}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.approvedGrossMargin}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{this.tlRemarks}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
            <tr style="background-color: #e8e8e8; font-weight: bold;">
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Total</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{data.totalApprovedFinalPrice}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{data.totalApprovedReceipt}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">{{data.totalApprovedBudget}}</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">—</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid #444; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">—</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>
        The tender due date and time is
        {{data.due_date_time}}. Please submit the tender at least 24 hours before the tender due date and time.
    </p>

    <p>Best Regards,<br />{{data.tl_name}}</p>
</div>